        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/g/b5e925/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-01-08T20:08:58.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I had the 1970 Montrose earlier this year with a group of wine friends and most people liked the '70 more the 1990 Montrose we drank alongside it.  It sure seemed that the 1970 could go another ten years.</p>",
