        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/k/b9bd4f/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-01-08T20:39:20.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thanks, guys. The fills on my 75s are almost too good to be true. (Maybe a separate string: \u201cDid Rudy ever waste his time on something as pedestrian as 70s Montrose?\u201d)</p>\n<p>I have had one bottle of the most killer 1970 Montrose, and also a completely DOA 1970. As they say, only good <em>bottles</em>\u2026</p>",
